               stealing on the <rs id="t18280410-44-cd256" type="crimeDate">26th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-44-off255 t18280410-44-cd256"></join>, one 10l. Bank-note the property of 
                     <persName id="t18280410-44-victim388" type="victimName">
                        George 
                        Wheeler
                     <interp inst="t18280410-44-victim388" type="surname" value="Wheeler"></interp>
